    # "A few minutes later, I'm eating dinner with my mom and dad… and Joan."
    "Alguns minutos depois, estou a jantar com a minha mãe e o meu pai… e a Joan."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:8
translate portuguese u19a1s3_ce706d43:

    # joan "So, where did you say you were from?"
    joan "Então, de onde é que disseste que eras?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:9
translate portuguese u19a1s3_b49e1c94:

    # pc "Oh, it's pretty far away."
    pc "Oh, é bastante longe."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:10
translate portuguese u19a1s3_c7dd76ae:

    # joan "Does this far away place have a name?"
    joan "Esse lugar tão longe tem um nome?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:11
translate portuguese u19a1s3_bb3bf43b:

    # pc "Um… Baltimore?"
    pc "Hum… Baltimore?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:14
translate portuguese u19a1s3_29fbf570:

    # joan "Never heard of it. Who's ever heard of a balty moor? What does that even mean?"
    joan "Nunca ouvi falar. Quem é que já ouviu falar de um «balty moor»? O que é que isso sequer significa?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:15
translate portuguese u19a1s3_afb14d41:

    # rm "You said your mother died when you were young and you're looking for your father… do you have any other family?"
    rm "Disseste que a tua mãe morreu quando eras jovem e que estás à procura do teu pai... tens mais família?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:16
translate portuguese u19a1s3_ac678886:

    # pc "No. That's it. It was just me and Dad."
    pc "Não. É só isso. Éramos só eu e o pai."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:17
translate portuguese u19a1s3_ef33ee14:

    # pc "Although I'd been living with a woman and her daughter for a while. They're almost like family."
    pc "Embora tenha vivido com uma mulher e a filha dela durante algum tempo. São quase como família."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:18
translate portuguese u19a1s3_c03433aa:

    # joan "You live with two women who aren't your family? Scandalous."
    joan "Vives com duas mulheres que não são da tua família? Escandaloso."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:21
translate portuguese u19a1s3_976801d0:

    # dad "How are they handling this? These two women?"
    dad "Como é que elas estão a lidar com isto? Estas duas mulheres?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:22
translate portuguese u19a1s3_9bf21394:

    # pc "They're managing. Both of them cared about my dad and when he went missing, they were both hurt."
    pc "Estão a aguentar-se. Ambas gostavam do meu pai e, quando ele desapareceu, ficaram ambas magoadas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:24
translate portuguese u19a1s3_67203c03:

    # pc "But I've been taking care of them."
    pc "Mas tenho cuidado delas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:27
translate portuguese u19a1s3_c7cf365b:

    # dad "I'm glad that you are there for them. I guess you'll be getting back to them soon?"
    dad "Fico contente por estares lá para elas. Suponho que vais voltar para junto delas em breve?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:28
translate portuguese u19a1s3_54f71631:

    # pc "Yeah, I think I'll head back tomorrow."
    pc "Sim, acho que vou voltar amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:31
translate portuguese u19a1s3_55466b20:

    # rm "So soon? I thought you were looking for your father in town?"
    rm "Tão cedo? Pensava que estavas à procura do teu pai na cidade?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:32
translate portuguese u19a1s3_8f8099ff:

    # pc "I was. But I'm starting to think that wherever he is, he's happier there."
    pc "Estava. Mas começo a pensar que, onde quer que ele esteja, é mais feliz lá."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:35
translate portuguese u19a1s3_3f17d1b6:

    # pc "I'll miss him, but I'm glad that he's happy."
    pc "Vou sentir a falta dele, mas fico contente por ele estar feliz."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:36
translate portuguese u19a1s3_6af4f214:

    # pc "I have people at home who need me though. I should go back to them."
    pc "Mas tenho pessoas em casa que precisam de mim. Devo voltar para junto delas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:37
translate portuguese u19a1s3_19f4cd3d:

    # rm "Well, I hope he's okay, wherever he is."
    rm "Bem, espero que ele esteja bem, onde quer que esteja."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:40
translate portuguese u19a1s3_7ebf47d4:

    # dad "I'm sure he is."
    dad "Tenho a certeza de que está."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:41
translate portuguese u19a1s3_5e85f982:

    # "Looking at the two of them together, I know that I could never pull them apart."
    "Ao olhar para os dois juntos, sei que nunca os conseguiria separar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:42
translate portuguese u19a1s3_b32eebbf:

    # "Entire worlds, death, and the laws of physics couldn't keep them apart."
    "Nem mundos inteiros, nem a morte, nem as leis da física conseguiriam separá-los."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:45
translate portuguese u19a1s3_0eae9cf7:

    # "I feel a foot touching my leg, making its way slowly and sensually up."
    "Sinto um pé a tocar-me na perna, subindo lentamente e de forma sensual."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:48
translate portuguese u19a1s3_d474497c:

    # "While Mom and Dad seem focused on each other, Joan gives me a flirty smile."
    "Enquanto a mãe e o pai parecem concentrados um no outro, a Joan lança-me um sorriso sedutor."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:51
translate portuguese u19a1s3_bfe3797c:

    # rm "Well, if you're leaving tomorrow, I'll make a care package for you. You'll need some food and gear for your travels."
    rm "Bem, se vais partir amanhã, vou preparar-te um pacote de provisões. Vais precisar de comida e de equipamento para a viagem."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:52
translate portuguese u19a1s3_cc5f8cab:

    # pc "Oh, I don't think I'll need too much. Thank you though."
    pc "Oh, acho que não vou precisar de muito. Mas obrigado na mesma."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:53
translate portuguese u19a1s3_d40c4415:

    # rm "You'll at least need a good night of sleep. You can stay here with us."
    rm "Vais precisar, pelo menos, de uma boa noite de sono. Podes ficar aqui connosco."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:56
translate portuguese u19a1s3_95b02b4e:

    # joan "He can stay in my room with me."
    joan "Ele pode ficar no meu quarto comigo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:57
translate portuguese u19a1s3_6616f112:

    # dad "I don't think so."
    dad "Acho que não."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:58
translate portuguese u19a1s3_9028272c:

    # rm "We have a spare bed we can set up in the storage room."
    rm "Temos uma cama extra que podemos arranjar na arrecadação."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:59
translate portuguese u19a1s3_2f5254ee:

    # dad "Yes, I think that will do nicely."
    dad "Sim, acho que isso vai servir muito bem."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene3.rpy:62
translate portuguese u19a1s3_030b7813:

    # pc "Thank you. That sounds great."
    pc "Obrigado. Parece-me ótimo."

